unisWIPSIgnoreListCfgEntry OBJECT-TYPE
    SYNTAX UnisWIPSIgnoreListCfgEntry
    MAX-ACCESS not-accessible
    STATUS current
    DESCRIPTION
        "Each entry contains information of each MAC address in the ignore list.
        "
    INDEX { unisWIPSIgnoreListMAC }
