unisWIPSSigPolicyEntry OBJECT-TYPE
    SYNTAX UnisWIPSSigPolicyEntry
    MAX-ACCESS not-accessible
    STATUS current
    DESCRIPTION
        "Each entry contains information of each signature policy."
